    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen boasts a pristine Getrag six-speed manual transmission and the factory variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural integrity. The chassis dynamics remain razor-sharp, supported by untouched factory bushings and impeccable suspension geometry. With showroom-quality aesthetics and a comprehensive service history, this is a turn-key example for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
